{"tid":2478671,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知呢隻係乜蟲","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T08:49:06.000Z","uid":11936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8ac5b75c9d45defa41d80f642f03e6ae4d29a9","tid":2478671,"uid":11936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"最近屋企出現左好多呢隻蟲仔<br />\n有啲綠色有啲黑色好似蚊之咁<br />\n每日一番黎就5-10隻係個窗角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一次殺十幾隻都仲有 <br />\n最弊有啲係窗外面又殺唔到<br />\n又唔知佢係邊生蛋<br />\n針就冇針但飛得好快一停即飛個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知叫乜想google下都唔得<br />\n有冇動物界巴打知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQwTkuNgB3dQXL1EMhRxH1tj5E6qNTxk7R16VQ8tZKSQa?filename=Nbs6BHR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbs6BHR.png&h=b7a321c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nps雖然影落好暗但佢是綠色的<br />\n好難影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664a1760be0a84ff64ef2e30cbbe95509c16968c","tid":2478671,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"似係昆蟲"},{"pid":"6585c7aea3ca94c2177422d488e709e739d68b9d","tid":2478671,"uid":29523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"準備定身後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d3dc5449242d6927d31856153cb71fc4a86aef","tid":2478671,"uid":313187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"664a1760be0a84ff64ef2e30cbbe95509c16968c","tid":2478671,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"似係昆蟲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:43:15.000Z","msg":"多謝晒"},{"pid":"08b2fce216f4624e2f74749adbb8126785c68563","tid":2478671,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:45:34.000